article.description: Chasity Clayton scored 13 points, Christian Hunnicutt added 10 and Florida State beat rival Florida 66-62.
article.headline: Clayton, Hunnicutt help Florida State rally past Florida
article.linkText: No. 10 Florida State rallies late to beat Florida
article.story:
GAINESVILLE, Fla. -- Chasity Clayton scored 13 points, Christian Hunnicutt added 10 and Florida State (No. 10 ESPN/USA Today, No. 13 AP) beat rival Florida 66-62 on Tuesday night.

The Gators (1-1) led 62-60 with 2:02 to play, but the Seminoles scored the last six points of the game. Alexa Deluzio's jumper with 37.4 seconds left made it 64-62.

Jacinta Monroe finished with nine points and 11 rebounds for Florida State (2-0).

Sharielle Smith led Florida with 18 points and 13 boards. The Gators were just 9-of-31 from behind the arc. Jordan Jones added with 13 points and five assists for Florida. She had a chance to tie the game at 65, but her shot from the top of the arc clanged off the basket with seven seconds left.
